  "texts": [
    "Participants were offered the opportunity to enter a prize draw for an iPad or a $US50 Amazon shopping voucher as an incentive to respond.",
    "A snowballing approach was used, where recipients were encouraged to forward the survey to colleagues who may be interested in responding.",
    "The data collection period extended from 24th of January to 9th of March 2023, during which time GPT3.5 was the prevailing model.",
    "A total of 763 survey responses were received.",
    "After excluding incomplete, non-English, and disingenuous responses, there were 318 participant responses remaining in the sample that were used as the basis of the analysis."
  ],
